<br>
I am a recent arrival on the FV. (I should say re-arrival... I leveled up an enchanter here back in the Fall of 2001 and then went back to blue-bie land).<br>
<br>
Anyhow, I have returned to FV! I haven't gotten around to making a new ez board account yet...<br>
<br>
Well, I'd like to say I am looking forward to being back here. I do not stress the population issues. There is nothing to stress. People come. People will go. Others will come. <br>
<br>
Planning is the key when finding a group sometimes. In the high-end of the game, as many know, &quot;pick up&quot; groups are usually lousy and many zones there are no pick up groups. So, if you are finding troubles getting groups, set a time and place with your friends and guild mates for the next hunt. Even if you get two or three to show up the next day, that is a solid beginning to any group.<br>
<br>
I love FV and the rule set. I find the bind rule annoying (hehe), but I can live with it. I LOVE LOVE LOVE no /ooc. A totally abused chat channel.<br>
<br>
Well, folks, I don't know if the server population is going down, or going up or moving left or right.. I don't care.. but I do care that there seems to be some really nice and cool people here and I am glad to be here again.<br>
<br>
Starting off as a &quot;newb&quot; is hard, but I embrace the challenge! See you all in game hopefully <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
