<br>
I myself would be 50 now save for the fact Scratchy and I have researched MANY zones and have been raiding 1-2 new ones per week.  We are hitting the zones we can raid as a duo.  I have solo raided zones.  We are doing quests for our level and concentrating on things like that. <br>
<br>
